---
title: Tarragon Chicken with Crushed Potatoes and Redcurrant Sauce
description: Our chefs have been creating recipes for a while now and one thing they’ve learnt along the way is that chicken, tarragon and buttery potatoes are a flavour combination that our customers absolutely love. Butterflying is a really useful technique to create an even thickness throughout a piece of meat so that it cooks quickly and evenly - perfect for those evenings when you’re a little short on time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tarragon-chicken-725aee7d-b7189d41.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/tarragon-chicken-5abe3b66ae08b5731e1e3752-06fce297.pdf
